data.description: Beautiful and full of character, 5 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home with lots of trees and beautifully landscaped fenced backyard. Two level deck, and newly installed gas fireplace. Expanded area game room/bedroom with custom high-grade LED beams. Large master bedroom with tray ceilings. Four bedrooms up. Master bath has whirlpool tub with separate walk-in shower and double sinks. All bedrooms are good size. Storage building, 16 x 16 stone paved area for wood burning fire pit, basketball goal or gazebo.
